<td tEditID="c1r2" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r2" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.38;">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;" id="docs-internal-guid-faa25597-493d-8b8b-51fc-161f3811e0c6"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Welcome back! We are delighted to invite you to return to your role as a {!Job_Application__c.Role_to_assess_for__c} for the 2016 NCS programme. </font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2"><br></font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2"><b>DBS applications</b></font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;">In order to undertake a role on our programme it is an absolute requirement that candidates have a valid enhanced DBS certificate with children's barred list issued on or after <b>1st January 2015. </b>Applicants who have not completed this process cannot be prioritised for placement and allocation. The process of obtaining this certification is fully funded by The Challenge and<b> </b><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/2016DBSinstructionspostoffer.pdf">full instructions of the application process can be found here</a><b>.</b></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Arial; font-size: small;">If you already have a valid DBS certificate that meets the above criteria then you will be able to upload this within the essential information section of the website. For more information about DBS certificates and applications please visit our </span><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/frequently-asked-questions/" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;">FAQs</a>.</p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b><font size="2">Essential Information</font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b><br></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><font size="2">Each section of the Essential Information page should be completed before you start your role. This includes:</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><font size="2"><br></font></p><ul style="font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline;"><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><font size="2"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Providing contact details for </span><span style="font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">2 referees</span></font></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline;"><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><font size="2"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Making a </span><span style="font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">tax declaration</span><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> and providing your </span><span style="font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">bank details </span><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">(from April)</span></font></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline;"><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><font size="2"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Filling out our </span><span style="font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">health, safeguarding &amp; inclusion</span><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> form</span></font></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline;"><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><font size="2"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Providing details for your </span><span style="font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">emergency contact</span></font></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline;"><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><font size="2"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Checking your </span><span style="font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">DBS status</span></font></p></li></ul><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b><br></b></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Availability and Training</b></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">You'll now also have access to the 'Choosing when I can work', 'Dates when I can't work' and 'My summary' pages. Here, you'll be able to choose which work dates you'd like to be considered for, and let us know of any dates when you won't be available to work.&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">The sooner we have this information, the sooner we'll be able to provisionally allocate you to a work placement.</span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;"><br></span></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">The 'Booking Training' page is also now open - here, you'll find a choice of dates to choose from for your day of returner training. This training is compulsory, and we can't let you work on the programme without it. Our training sessions fill up fast - login and book your training as soon as possible to secure your place!</font></div><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.38;">Any questions?</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">As ever, if you have any questions about the programme or your application, please donâ€™t hesitate to get in touch with your </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/contact/">local staffing team</a></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">. Information is also available on our </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/frequently-asked-questions/">FAQs</a></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">. </span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><br></span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">We look forward to working with you again in 2016!</span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><br></span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">{!Contact.OwnerFullName}</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span id="docs-internal-guid-faa25597-4941-6fb7-f456-85de347c9ccf"></span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">{!Contact.Contact_Owner_alternative_email__c}</font></span></p>]]></td>
